description: Returns a list of RepositorySummary objects. Each RepositorySummary contains information about a repository in the specified Amazon Web Services account and that matches the input parameters.

nested_items.name: repositories
nested_items.description: The returned list of RepositorySummary objects.

nested_items.name: administratorAccount
nested_items.description: The Amazon Web Services account ID that manages the repository.

nested_items.name: domainName
nested_items.description: The name of the domain that contains the repository.

nested_items.name: domainOwner
nested_items.description: The 12-digit account number of the Amazon Web Services account that owns the domain. It does not include dashes or spaces.

nested_items.name: createdTime
nested_items.description: A timestamp that represents the date and time the repository was created.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: If there are additional results, this is the token for the next set of results.
